text: Happy happy birthday to my best friend.
Look how much fun he has!
I am in love with him…
A day without you, is a day wasted…
Missing you. Every second. It hurts.
His fur shines very nicely since he gets new food
Who let the dogs out? Who, who, who, who, who
I love to work from home with my dog. He helps me keeping motivated.
Don't worry, be happy with my dog.
Happy as long as I am with you.
